      "pyCode": "def NoOverlappingIntegration():\n    for t in integrating:\n        for u in integrating:\n            if t != u and len([p for p in SCOPE[t] if p in SCOPE[u]]) > 0:\n                return False\n    return True\n\n# S2 \u2014 at most one integration onto the head at a time (queue.Mutex).\n"
